      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it does show clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has various minor scratches, some noticeable paint fading on the roof and hood, and a small ding on the passenger side door. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, but all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, it has been regularly serviced and runs well, though buyers should expect the typical maintenance needs associated with a car of this age.",
