    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. Honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride and has never let me down! It\u2019s in really solid shape and still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it runs smoothly and is ready to hit the pavement for its next adventure. It has a few minor signs of love from regular trips, but it\u2019s overall a super dependable and comfy vehicle. If you\u2019re looking for a great deal on a car that\u2019s got plenty of life left, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 32500.0,
