    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six engine equipped with six individual throttle bodies and a dual-overhead-cam valvetrain. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a factory GKN limited-slip differential. The double-VANOS variable valve timing system has been meticulously maintained, ensuring a linear power band up to the 7,900 RPM redline. The chassis benefits from a multi-link rear suspension and reinforced subframe mounting points, maintaining the structural rigidity required for high-lateral-G cornering. While the aesthetics show honest wear consistent with a well-maintained driver, the powertrain remains in peak operational status with recent valve clearances and cooling system refreshes. This is a visceral, analog machine optimized for technical driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
