    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for vehicle that perfectly balances performance with daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only the minor, honest signs of road use one would expect from a well-loved car. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin with plush, intact seating and a fully functional dashboard where every button and dial operates as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound; it has been serviced at regular intervals, with recent oil changes and brake inspections already completed. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the engine delivers consistent, smooth power. This is a turn-key opportunity for a driver seeking a reliable, attractive vehicle that has been treated with respect. Detailed service logs are available for your review.",
